_metadata.description: Find top performing companies by Return on Assets
_metadata.original_query: SELECT c.display_name, c.segment, m.Return_on_Assets, m.Net_Profit_Margin_Percentage FROM new_financial_metrics m JOIN new_company_info c ON m.company_name = c.company WHERE m.year = 2023 AND m.Return_on_Assets IS NOT NULL ORDER BY m.Return_on_Assets DESC LIMIT 10

_metadata.description: Get liquidity ratios for companies
_metadata.original_query: SELECT c.display_name, c.segment, m.Current_Ratio, m.Quick_Ratio, m.Debt_to_Equity FROM new_financial_metrics m JOIN new_company_info c ON m.company_name = c.company WHERE m.year = 2023 AND m.Current_Ratio IS NOT NULL ORDER BY m.Current_Ratio DESC LIMIT 10
